195
00:12:45,950 --> 00:12:48,480
If you do this, will she take it seriously?

196
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:50,340
You don't get it.

197
00:12:50,340 --> 00:12:53,640
Your mom's been in the hospital for a year. She's seen all kinds of chaos and drama.

198
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:56,260
Ordinary surprises don't work on her.

199
00:12:56,260 --> 00:12:59,540
I tell you, you must follow my orders later.

200
00:12:59,540 --> 00:13:03,740
As soon as your mom comes home in a sorrowful mood,

201
00:13:03,740 --> 00:13:05,780
we rush up and give her a big hug.

202
00:13:05,780 --> 00:13:08,860
That's what we call a surprise. What do you think?

203
00:13:08,860 --> 00:13:10,340
- All right. 
 - Let's do it.

204
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:11,890
Let's go.

205
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:15,580
   

206
00:13:15,580 --> 00:13:18,080
   

207
00:13:29,410 --> 00:13:32,260
Didn't you say she went to the hospital for a quick visit?

208
00:13:32,260 --> 00:13:35,000
We've been waiting for so long. Why isn't she back yet?

209
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,700
I don't know.

210
00:13:36,700 --> 00:13:38,800
My back hurts. Keep an eye out for me. I need a break.

211
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:40,920
All right. Go ahead, Dad.

212
00:13:50,775 --> 00:13:52,400
Dad! She's here! She's here!

213
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:54,380
Hurry!

214
00:13:54,380 --> 00:13:56,140
Move!

215
00:13:56,140 --> 00:13:58,200
Hide! Hide! Hide!

216
00:14:04,620 --> 00:14:06,880
   

217
00:14:22,660 --> 00:14:25,920
   

218
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:29,680
Chen Lei! Give me back my daughter!

219
00:14:29,680 --> 00:14:31,690
What's happening?

220
00:14:32,540 --> 00:14:35,020
- Oh no, we messed up. 
 - Oh my goodness.

221
00:14:35,020 --> 00:14:37,540
- Mom! Mom! 
 - Li Na! Li Na! Li Na!

222
00:14:37,540 --> 00:14:39,110
Chen Lei!

223
00:14:39,110 --> 00:14:41,290
Huan Er!

224
00:14:41,290 --> 00:14:42,710
Li Na!

225
00:14:42,710 --> 00:14:44,000
Li Na!

226
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,590
- Mom! Mom! 
 - Li Na!

227
00:14:45,590 --> 00:14:47,280
Mom!

228
00:14:47,280 --> 00:14:50,110
Why did you come back? Why did you even come back?

229
00:14:50,110 --> 00:14:51,920
Get your filthy hands off me! I tell you...

230
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:53,660
Take this!

231
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:57,090
You two are too much! You scared me a lot.

232
00:14:57,090 --> 00:14:59,370
- What is this? 
 - Look!

233
00:15:01,850 --> 00:15:04,080
Why don't you hang a banner for me too?

234
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:05,492
- Oh, right, Dad! 
 - We forgot the banner.

235
00:15:05,492 --> 00:15:06,700
I'll get a banner next time!

236
00:15:06,700 --> 00:15:07,790
- Hurry up! 
 - Sit down!

237
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:09,950
You two are too much!

238
00:15:09,950 --> 00:15:11,610
- Mom, don't be angry. 
 - We were just joking.

239
00:15:11,610 --> 00:15:14,050
Huan Er, put this on your mom. Come on, come on.

240
00:15:14,050 --> 00:15:15,950
- I'm not wearing that! 
 - Come on, put it on!

241
00:15:15,950 --> 00:15:18,880
So pretty! How beautiful!

242
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:20,920
Look here. Ready?

243
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:23,140
- I don't want! 
 - Just take a look. Just take a look.

244
00:15:23,140 --> 00:15:25,900
One, two, three.

245
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:46,860
 Sister, after thinking about it, I want to change back to the previous cake. Can I? 

246
00:15:46,860 --> 00:15:48,550
 Sure! 

247
00:16:05,380 --> 00:16:08,110
Honey, happy birthday!

248
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:10,450
Dad picked this one out himself.

249
00:16:10,450 --> 00:16:11,830
This looks pretty nice.

250
00:16:11,830 --> 00:16:13,100
Look.

251
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:14,840
Come on, let's celebrate the birthday.

252
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,920
Look at you. How could you take it seriously?

253
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:18,500
Wasn't it just a joke?

254
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:20,380
What joke? That was a scare, okay?

255
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:21,950
Fine, a scare. Sorry, sorry.

256
00:16:21,950 --> 00:16:25,090
Light the candles.

257
00:16:26,130 --> 00:16:31,860
♪  Happy birthday to you  ♪

