00:16:35,020 --> 00:16:38,120
♪  Happy birthday to me  ♪

260
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,040
Make a wish, make a wish.

261
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:41,580
Make a wish. Mom, make a wish.

262
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,730
Blow out the candles.

263
00:16:46,610 --> 00:16:48,530
All right.

264
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:51,330
- Mom. 
 - Look how nice it is.

265
00:16:51,330 --> 00:16:54,760
I prepared a birthday present for you.

266
00:16:54,760 --> 00:16:58,090
- Look. This is the one I prepared. 
 - There's even a birthday gift!

267
00:16:58,090 --> 00:17:00,570
Mom, open it and see.

268
00:17:05,050 --> 00:17:08,320
Inside... you're the star of every photo.

269
00:17:08,320 --> 00:17:10,090
You learned this from Jing Xi Chi, right?

270
00:17:10,090 --> 00:17:12,020
Not very original.

271
00:17:12,020 --> 00:17:14,130
- Yeah. 
 - I went through our family photos,

272
00:17:14,130 --> 00:17:16,090
but I couldn't find many pictures of you both.

273
00:17:16,090 --> 00:17:18,300
You were always busy taking pictures of me.

274
00:17:18,300 --> 00:17:20,170
From now on, I'll take more pictures of you both.

275
00:17:20,170 --> 00:17:21,900
Oh, you're mistaken.

276
00:17:21,900 --> 00:17:25,680
Your mom used to have more than a dozen photo albums. They were all lost when we moved.

277
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:27,600
All that's left is...

278
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:31,130
♪  Happy birthday!  ♪

279
00:17:31,130 --> 00:17:32,500
Mom, do you like it?

280
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,900
- Does it look nice? 
 - How about this one?

281
00:17:33,900 --> 00:17:35,160
Isn't it nice?

282
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,890
Come on, let's eat cake.

283
00:17:36,890 --> 00:17:38,990
Don't just eat cake.

284
00:17:38,990 --> 00:17:40,530
I'll cook some noodles.

285
00:17:40,530 --> 00:17:42,630
Let me do it. You don't have to.

286
00:17:42,630 --> 00:17:46,790
You just stay and cut the cake. Let me do it. I'll do it.

287
00:17:46,790 --> 00:17:54,810
 Just as I expected, my parents' argument ended without any danger this time. 

288
00:17:54,810 --> 00:18:02,000
 Now I finally understand that only when love is deep enough can one argue 

289
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,850
 with such confidence. 

290
00:18:03,850 --> 00:18:08,010
 That's their unique kind of romance. 

291
00:18:12,780 --> 00:18:15,440
- Why did you call me here? 
 - You'll know when you see it.

292
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:17,530
I'm full. I don't feel like moving.

293
00:18:17,530 --> 00:18:18,720
- Hurry up. 
 - I feel bloated.

294
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:20,870
Go up there! Sit there.

295
00:18:20,870 --> 00:18:22,670
Here. Sit here.

296
00:18:22,670 --> 00:18:24,520
What are you doing?

297
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:26,000
Close your eyes.

298
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:28,480
Close your eyes.

299
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:32,000
Have you already closed your eyes?

300
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,620
Don't open your eyes unless I tell you to.

301
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:36,180
Don't open your eyes. You must not open your eyes.

302
00:18:37,330 --> 00:18:38,810
- Are you cheating? 
 - No.

303
00:18:38,810 --> 00:18:40,130
No peeking! Close your eyes.

304
00:18:40,130 --> 00:18:42,640
- I got it. 
 - No peeking.

305
00:18:46,050 --> 00:18:48,270
Chen Huan Er!

306
00:18:48,270 --> 00:18:49,720
No peeking!

307
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:52,130
I'm watching you. Don't try to peek.

308
00:18:52,130 --> 00:18:55,240
I'm watching you. Don't open your eyes yet. I'm still watching you.

309
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:58,090
- What exactly are you up to? 
 - You'll find out soon.

310
00:18:58,090 --> 00:19:00,080
Stop talking.

311
00:19:00,080 --> 00:19:02,000
Don't open your eyes.

312
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:08,660
Stretch out your hand.

313
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:10,540
Stretch out your hand.

314
00:19:12,500 --> 00:19:14,300
No peeking. You still can't open your eyes yet.

315
00:19:14,300 --> 00:19:15,970
- Wait a while. 
 - I didn't peek.

316
00:19:15,970 --> 00:19:17,440
Don't open your eyes.

317
00:19:18,870 --> 00:19:21,160
What's that sound?

318
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,770
Open your eyes.

319
00:19:35,390 --> 00:19:37,220
This...

320
00:19:37,220 --> 00:19:40,236
Didn't they say they don't sell this cake in slices?

321
00:19:40,236 --> 00:19:43,460
This is just a small problem that won't defeat me.

322
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:50,920
Look at you. You wanted to eat it, didn't you?

323
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:54,480
Since you want to eat it, of course you should have it.

324
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:59,390
How did you settle this?

325
00:20:02,050 --> 00:20:03,090
 Hi. 

326
00:20:03,090 --> 00:20:06,440
 Could you get me the cake from the display rack and cut it into three pieces? 

327
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:08,160
 Okay, wait a moment. 

328
00:20:09,580 --> 00:20:11,140
 - What's the big deal? 
 - Why did you call me over? 

329
00:20:11,140 --> 00:20:13,727
 What are you doing? 

330
00:20:13,727 --> 00:20:16,870
 Back at Sishui, didn't Aunt Hao like eating cake? 

331
00:20:16,870 --> 00:20:19,400
 Take this cake back for her. She'd be so happy. 

332
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:21,710
 But you guys didn’t invite me there. Why drag me into this? 

333
00:20:21,710 --> 00:20:23,400
 I'm not accepting your bribe. 

334
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:26,470
 Buddy, I'm not bribing you. 

335
00:20:26,470 --> 00:20:27,870
 I was just thinking of you. 

336
00:20:27,870 --> 00:20:30,240
 Look, Dr. Li worries about you every day. 

337
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:32,820
 Shouldn't you do something to show your filial piety? 

338
00:20:32,820 --> 00:20:34,560
 Am I right? 

339
00:20:34,560 --> 00:20:36,280
 I've finished packing. 

340
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,870
 Thank you. 

341
00:20:38,870 --> 00:20:41,230
 - You two, remember to pay. 
 - What? 

342
00:20:45,950 --> 00:20:47,910
 158 yuan. 

343
00:20:50,530 --> 00:20:51,990
 Do you have... 

344
00:20:51,990 --> 00:20:54,110
 How much do you have? 

345
00:20:55,570 --> 00:20:57,350
 38 yuan. 

346
00:21:05,500 --> 00:21:07,000
 Not enough. 

347
00:21:07,580 --> 00:21:09,200
 Still 20 yuan short. 

348
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:11,260
 Just 20 yuan more. 

349
00:21:13,770 --> 00:21:15,290
 I have no more left. 

350
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:18,360
 - We'll just take one. 
 - Can we pay next time? 

351
00:21:22,580 --> 00:21:26,230
Why do you ask so many questions? Just eat it.

352
00:21:28,780 --> 00:21:30,390
There's even a candle.

353
00:21:30,390 --> 00:21:32,870
It's not my birthday today.

354
00:21:32,870 --> 00:21:35,020
Who cares if it's your birthday or not?

355
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:37,820
I say it's your birthday, so it is.

356
00:21:37,820 --> 00:21:39,998
Happy birthday.

357
00:21:39,998 --> 00:21:42,360
Don't cry.

358
00:21:42,360 --> 00:21:44,110
Close your eyes.

359
00:21:46,470 --> 00:21:48,750
Make a wish.

360
00:21:48,750 --> 00:21:50,060
Make a wish.

361
00:21:50,060 --> 00:21:52,760
Blow out the candle after making a wish.

362
00:22:08,150 --> 00:22:09,780
Thank you.

363
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:16,910
It must be very delicious.

364
00:22:16,910 --> 00:22:18,360
Eat it.

365
00:22:18,360 --> 00:22:20,230
Why is there only one?

366
00:22:20,230 --> 00:22:23,060
I bought this for you. I'm not eating. You eat it.

367
00:22:24,080 --> 00:22:27,130
Here, hold it. Eat it.

368
00:22:33,490 --> 00:22:35,160
How is it?

369
00:22:35,160 --> 00:22:37,870
- This is delicious, right? 
 - It's so good.

370
00:22:38,710 --> 00:22:40,740
- You try a bite too. 
 - I don't want to.

371
00:22:40,740 --> 00:22:42,920
- Just try one. 
 - I find you gross.

372
00:22:42,920 --> 00:22:45,020
I don't even mind you, and you mind me?

373
00:22:45,020 --> 00:22:47,230
Try it, it's really good.

374
00:22:47,230 --> 00:22:48,880
Is it good?

375
00:22:50,100 --> 00:22:52,080
- It's really delicious! 
 - Yummy, right?

376
00:22:52,080 --> 00:22:54,160
No wonder it's so expensive.

377
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:56,870
Is this pricey?

378
00:22:56,870 --> 00:22:59,440
Not really. I got it covered. Eat up.

379
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:01,320
Then, take another bite.

380
00:23:17,770 --> 00:23:20,810
Mom, I got you a cake. Try it.

381
00:23:20,810 --> 00:23:24,720
Son, you finally know how to care for your mom.

382
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:28,460
All right, I'll go and cut it. We'll eat it together.

383
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:32,060
- You're back. 
 - Mom.

384
00:23:32,060 --> 00:23:33,514
What did you buy?

385
00:23:33,514 --> 00:23:35,580
The cake shop had a discount, so I bought some for you.

386
00:23:35,580 --> 00:23:38,260
We just ate. Isn't that a waste of money?

387
00:23:38,260 --> 00:23:40,806
- Look. 
 - Let me see.

388
00:23:40,806 --> 00:23:42,020
Song Hang.

389
00:23:42,020 --> 00:23:44,620
- This is nice. 
 - Dad, come and have some.

390
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:56,150
 Are you done taking photos? 

391
00:23:56,150 --> 00:23:57,380
 Yeah, it's done. 

392
00:23:57,380 --> 00:23:59,340
 Your camera is nice. It's made in Germany, right? 

393
00:23:59,340 --> 00:24:00,640
 - Let's go dancing. 
 - Hurry. 

394
00:24:00,640 --> 00:24:01,780
 This is nice. 

395
00:24:01,780 --> 00:24:03,430
 Let's go. 

396
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:07,670
 Just loosen up a bit when we're there, okay? 

397
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:11,540
 There he is. 

398
00:24:15,190 --> 00:24:16,720
 You came so early. 

399
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:19,810
 I came a bit earlier to save a seat for you. 

400
00:24:20,390 --> 00:24:22,090
 You're here, Yi Fan. 

401
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:24,950
 He's calling you Yi Fan now? 

402
00:24:24,950 --> 00:24:28,260
 Don't just stand there. Let's go dance. 

403
00:24:28,260 --> 00:24:31,000
 Come on! Come on! 

404
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:32,960
 I'll go and buy something to drink. 

405
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:34,540
 Song Hang, what do you want? 

406
00:24:34,540 --> 00:24:37,300
 - I'll go with you. 
 - All right. 

407
00:24:44,610 --> 00:24:47,430
 You usually dress like a gangster. 

408
00:24:47,430 --> 00:24:50,150
 Why are you dressed so properly today? 

409
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:56,910
 Didn't you say that running around playing soccer doesn't lead to much of a future? 

410
00:24:56,910 --> 00:24:59,840
 So, I decided to apply to the fire department. 

411
00:25:01,340 --> 00:25:03,780
 I was joking. 

412
00:25:03,780 --> 00:25:05,390
 Why did you take it seriously? 

413
00:25:05,390 --> 00:25:07,300
 I wasn't joking. 

414
00:25:07,300 --> 00:25:13,850
 Yi Fan, if I get into the fire department, will you seriously consider me then? 

415
00:25:27,370 --> 00:25:31,020
 The photos from last time are done. 

416
00:25:31,020 --> 00:25:33,710
 I brought the ones with you in them. 

417
00:25:33,710 --> 00:25:36,100
 You even carried them along with you? 

418
00:25:44,500 --> 00:25:49,518
 That day, when I went to your workplace to drop off photos for the juniors, 

419
00:25:49,518 --> 00:25:51,670
 I actually brought yours too. 

420
00:25:51,670 --> 00:25:54,740
 But it looked like you had swapped shifts. 

421
00:25:54,740 --> 00:25:56,060
 You weren't there. 

422
00:25:56,060 --> 00:25:58,130
 So... 

423
00:26:02,390 --> 00:26:04,020
 The pictures are so nice. 

424
00:26:04,020 --> 00:26:07,480
 You university students take photos differently. 

425
00:26:08,910 --> 00:26:10,670
 It's nothing. 

426
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,860
 Thank you. 

427
00:26:19,340 --> 00:26:23,500
♫  Love ya love  ♫

428
00:26:23,500 --> 00:26:27,260
♫  What really is love  ♫

