♫  Love ya love  ♫

432
00:26:39,832 --> 00:26:44,072
♫  Maybe one day she forgets love  ♫

433
00:26:44,072 --> 00:26:50,460
♫  Until she suddenly wakes up and learns to love  ♫

434
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:57,260
How are you doing at your workplace? Is your stomach still hurting?

435
00:26:58,610 --> 00:27:03,430
Listen to me, drink some warm water when you're free.

436
00:27:03,430 --> 00:27:06,330
Listen to the doctor's advice.

437
00:27:06,330 --> 00:27:10,300
I may be your wife, but I'm also a doctor.

438
00:27:11,030 --> 00:27:13,560
All right, I got it.

