00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:45,420
   

443
00:27:49,780 --> 00:27:56,721
 Hey... what do you think love was like for our parents back then? 

444
00:27:56,721 --> 00:27:59,840
 Maybe we'll understand it someday. 

445
00:27:59,840 --> 00:28:04,140
♫  Maybe you are still waiting  ♫

446
00:28:04,140 --> 00:28:08,340
♫  Wandering in a deep night  ♫

447
00:28:08,340 --> 00:28:15,060
♫  Those past memories feel like a dream but cannot be let go  ♫

448
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:20,960
♫  That young girl  ♫

449
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:24,600
♫  Maybe she never left  ♫

450
00:28:24,600 --> 00:28:27,760
♫  I think it is love  ♫

