00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:05,820
Look at you bragging.

582
00:38:06,830 --> 00:38:08,160
All right.

583
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:09,720
I got it.

584
00:38:12,520 --> 00:38:14,190
Don't give up.

585
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:17,620
I'm leaving.

586
00:38:42,380 --> 00:38:45,280
I've been looking for you two for a long time. It turns out you're sitting here.

587
00:38:45,280 --> 00:38:46,850
Come on.

588
00:38:46,850 --> 00:38:50,520
Recently, I had someone bring me some supplements from New Zealand.

589
00:38:50,520 --> 00:38:53,280
Kids are under a lot of academic stress lately. These are good for the brain.

590
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:56,260
Each of you, take one.

591
00:38:58,650 --> 00:39:04,210
Sister Li, you do know that supplements shouldn't be taken care of carelessly.

592
00:39:04,210 --> 00:39:06,290
Even medicine is three parts poison.

593
00:39:06,290 --> 00:39:11,040
For kids, just some basic vitamins will do. Understand?

594
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:13,120
Am I right, Yi Fan?

595
00:39:14,860 --> 00:39:17,040
What's wrong with you? Something on your mind?

596
00:39:17,040 --> 00:39:22,940
It's nothing. I'm just hesitating over whether I should ask you for

597
00:39:22,940 --> 00:39:25,230
