598
00:39:25,230 --> 00:39:28,150
Of course. Any level, any price range, you name it.

599
00:39:28,150 --> 00:39:33,370
Feel free to ask me. What happened? Are you thinking of getting Xi Chi a tutor?

600
00:39:35,180 --> 00:39:36,370
It's just...

601
00:39:36,370 --> 00:39:39,700
A while ago, I went to ask the sports university professors.

